gnal to calculate the accuracy of the approach. We conduct a set of\nexperiments on six adder architectures and four multiplier architectures. The\naverage error to calculate the rare nets between RTL simulation and estimated\nvalues are below 2% in all architectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Mar 2020 23:58:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-31"}
