ver-ionisation is an important NLTE mechanism are likely affected by\ndepartures from LTE in Mg . Special care must be taken with the collisions\nadopted for high-lying levels when calculating NLTE profiles of lines in the\nH-band. The derived NLTE corrections in the optical and in the H-band differ,\nbut the derived NLTE abundances are consistent between the two spectral\nregions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2020 11:35:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-20"}
