 and\nCGP-60474 have the potential as repurposed drugs for its treatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2020 03:36:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 May 2020 05:34:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-05"}
